# Deploy to:   /etc/audit/rules.d/99-hardening.rules  (append to hardening baseline)
# Apply:       augenrules --load  (restart auditd first if running with -e 2)
# Module:      file-transfer
# Requires:    hardening/self-managed/configs/audit/99-hardening.rules applied first
#
# Appends SFTP chroot path monitoring to the existing hardening audit ruleset.
# Parameters modified from baseline:  none — additive only

# ── SFTP — file-transfer ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
-w /srv/sftp/ -p rwa -k sftp_activity